components.templateData:

    headingTxt="Heading"
    subHeadingTxt="Subheading">

    (snippetEvent)="snippetClick($event)"></lib-uv-ui-snippet>
    
</lib-uv-ui-navbar-dashboard-sub>

components.templateData:
<button type="button"
        (click)="onClick($event)"
        [ngClass]="classes"
        [ngStyle]="{ 'background-color': backgroundColor }">
    {{ label }}
</button>
